# and start the providers when the integration tests (*ITestFX) run on the classpath. In a module-path
# build these come from each provider module's module-info `provides`; on the test classpath only these
# META-INF/services files are consulted. Lists only the providers framework depends on at test scope
# (ephemeral data store + entity/stamp + executor) — mirrors tinkar-core/integration's test resources.
